premise_source_doc_sentence: The eighth season of the tattoo reality competition Ink Master  (  subtitled as Ink Master : Peck vs. Nuñez  )  premiered on August 23 , 2016 on Spike .
The ninth season of the tattoo reality competition Ink Master  (  subtitled as Ink Master : Shop Wars  )  will premiere on June 6 , 2017 on Spike at 10/9c .
The eighth season of the tattoo reality competition Ink Master  (  subtitled as Ink Master : Peck vs. Nuñez  )  premiered on August 23 , 2016 on Spike .
The winner of this season will receive $ 200,000 , a feature in Inked magazine , and the title of both Ink Master and `` Master Shop ''
Season 9 will feature teams of two sorted by their tattoo shops going head-to-head for the first time in Ink Master history .
